{"tid":1568047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[借力打力] 一招瓦解港共組織力","createTime":"2019-09-14T08:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:57:57.000Z","uid":267494,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd0989ddc6233d854704befd31708bdf07d4f39","tid":1568047,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思,呃左你入黎,因為係有3招,加2個設計策略準則<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先講準則<br />\n<br />\n1. 群眾鬥群眾唔係壞事,能夠落實訴求固然好事,但唔成功我地就鬥到經濟攬炒, 而咁有組織既行動根本就應該要好好利用維持及擴大衝突, 即係利用對家行動, 給予社會對愛國行動本身會引來嚴重衝突既恐懼,最後令當區鋪頭落閘收工, 長期達到經濟攪炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 製造低質鏡頭送上支那, 分化及迷惑支那既愛國人士, 加大兩地予盾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n策略,我拋磚引玉講幾個<br />\n<br />\n1. 幫佢地既行動文宣加料, <span style=\"color: red;\">例如: 參加者應自備武器防身, 當天已知有黑衣人搞事</span><br />\n再幫佢地大量宣傳, 呢個係事實, 反正次次都係有手足自行送頭, 利用手足送頭, 起碼佢地既付出都有少少成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 掉國旗, 呢個唔洗我講, 佢地自己會掉, 不過你自己收集返再「幫」佢地掉入垃圾桶都得, 反正佢地都係當垃圾唔要, 又或者你事先準備十幾件, 但因為慘慘豬無人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 所以只能夠扔曬佢, 事後影張相後送上支那, 文字點演繹就係你既事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 黎一招終極捧殺<span style=\"color: red;\"> (核彈級,出招前要小心衡量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) </span>, 按現時發展, 相信好快會有納粹式愛中國連儂牆出現, 大家到時幫佢地一把, 用盡各種滅絕人性既說話文宣, 再盡力宣傳黑警會默許愛國人士所有既衝擊行動, 斷正都係HEA查加告最輕既罪(事實), 睇下揚開去之後香港係回復和平發展, 抑或攬炒等國際圍剿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我P牌仔, 但都希望大家認真諗如何借力打力, 利用對方既組織力, 攻心為上, 不戰而屈人之兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a23cb1ce4f36ad5a37e8a3e12f80c3d2f9f1db0","tid":1568047,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:10:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"802c117dc5ecba4ff857291e71e161aaaa8e3027","tid":1568047,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:12:42.000Z","msg":"P牌仔, 推唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f3674eced89987017854f6c20e4d05fcb69fe5","tid":1568047,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"0fc2bfda217e0a3f695f85909b97c36df9ad975f","tid":1568047,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"802c117dc5ecba4ff857291e71e161aaaa8e3027","tid":1568047,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:12:42.000Z","msg":"P牌仔, 推唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:17:16.000Z","msg":"唉, 次次認真呼籲都無人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8373703a49b37f78e6847b2bca25d72a77a7d59d","tid":1568047,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9e1a584e797a8b018691884ac6f8c96e91b78cbc","tid":1568047,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:19:22.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"f7d43af650c03bbd34453dd8683673d1a00fbd8e","tid":1568047,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a48ce6321